Rattrap:




Rattrap looked up and saw a flier soar by. It looked to be Sage Firestorm. 
He didn't like the feel of it. After a few seconds, he thought that Sage 
Firestorm and his little buddy may be going for that female mouse. He 
thought to himself just keep moving and keep away from the others as far as 
possible, but something contended. He found himself running after them. He 
knew it was stupid, but Primal influence was still with him.
